text: This transmits obsolete IRM 4.71.15, Employee Plans Examination of Returns, EP Special Review.

On April 1, 2017, Employee Plans Special Review underwent a reorganization and was transplanted to Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation, Issue Identiﬁcation and Special Review. In addition, Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation assumed ownership of this manual.

New IRM 4.70.7, TE/GE Examinations, Special Review (SR) and Tax Exempt Quality Measurement System (TEQMS) Procedures, supersedes this manual, rendering this manual obsolete. Please the new manual for all directions concerning special review for employee plans.
